            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <p class="info-text">优步为您的隐私保驾护航</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <input type="text" class="ipt" placeholder="请输入手机号码">
            </div>
            <div class="row flex-m">
                <button class="btn open-btn flip" onclick="$('#page2').hide();$('#page3').show();">立刻领取红包</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </sectiont>

    <sectiont class="page page3" id="page3" style="display: none">
        <img src="images/logo.png" alt="" class="fixed-logo">
        <div class="flex-1 flex-m">
            <div class="inner content">
                <p class="info-title">恭喜你抢到欧洲杯红包！</p>
                <img src="images/page3-icon.png" alt="" class="icon swing">
                <p class="info-msg">优惠券将在 <span>6月13日（星期一）</span></p>
                <p class="info-desc">自动存入您的账户中，立即可用</p>
                <p class="info-desc">*每人可享15程，每程最高减免5元，重庆主城有效</p>
                <div class="row flex-m">
                    <button class="btn bounceInLeft" onclick="$('#page2').hide();$('#page3').show();">立即注册领取乘车优惠券</button>
                </div>
                <div class="row flex-m">
                    <button class="btn bounceInLeft" onclick="$('#page2').hide();$('#page3').show();">一键获得30元</button>
                </div>
                <div class="row flex-m">
                    <button class="btn open-btn bounceInLeft" onclick="$('#page3').hide();$('#page7').show();">点击右上角分享给好友</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="row">
                <p class="info-msg">新用户输入优惠码<span>疯狂欧洲杯</span></p>
                <p class="info-desc">即可获得2程10元乘车优惠</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </sectiont>
    
    <sectiont class="page flex-m page4" id="page4" style="display: none">
        <img src="images/logo.png" alt="" class="fixed-logo">
        <div class="inner content">
            <p class="info-title">恭喜你抢到欧洲杯红包！</p>
            <img src="images/page3-icon.png" alt="" class="icon">
            <p class="info-msg">优惠券将在 <span>6月13日（星期一）</span></p>
            <p class="info-desc">自动存入您的账户中，立即可用</p>
            <p class="info-desc">*每人可享15程，每程最高减免5元，重庆主城有效</p>
            <div class="row flex-m">
                <button class="btn" onclick="$('#page2').hide();$('#page3').show();">一键获得30元</button>
            </div>
            <div class="row flex-m">
                <button class="btn open-btn" onclick="$('#page4').hide();$('#page7').show();"">点击右上角分享给好友</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </sectiont>

    <sectiont class="page page5" id="page5" style="display: none">
        <img src="images/logo.png" alt="" class="fixed-logo">
        <div class="flex-1 flex-m">
            <div class="inner content">
                <img src="images/page5-share.png" class="share">
                <img src="images/page5-icon.png" alt="" class="icon">
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="row">
                <p class="info-msg">新用户输入优惠码<span>疯狂欧洲杯</span></p>
                <p class="info-desc">即可获得2程10元乘车优惠</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </sectiont>

    
    <sectiont class="page flex-m page6" id="page6" style="display: none">
        <img src="images/logo.png" alt="" class="fixed-logo">
        <div class="inner content">
            <p class="info-title">红包已经被抢完啦！</p>
            <p class="info-title-large">想免费乘车？<span>可以</span></p>
            <img src="images/page6-icon.png" alt="" class="icon">
            <p class="info-msg">1、分享您的个人优惠码给好友 </p>
            <p class="info-msg">2、好友输入即可获得3次10元乘车优惠</p>
            <p class="info-msg">3、好友成功乘坐1次</p>
            <p class="info-desc">您就可立即获得3次10元乘车优惠！</p>
        </div>
    </sectiont>


    <sectiont class="page flex-m page7" id="page7" style="display: none">
        <img src="images/logo.png" alt="" class="fixed-logo">
        <div class="inner content">
            <img src="images/share-icon.png" class="share">
        </div>
    </sectiont>

    <sectiont class="page flex-m page8" id="page8" style="display: none">
        <img src="images/logo.png" alt="" class="fixed-logo">
        <div class="inner content">
            <div class="counter">
                <div class="fraction-box">
                    <ul class="fraction">
                        <li>0</li>
                        <li>0</li>
                        <li>0</li>
                        <li>0</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row flex-m">
                <button class="btn open-btn flip">活动时间:xxxx 敬请期待</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </sectiont>


</div>
<script src="vendor/zepto/zepto.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
        $("#page1Btn").click(function(){
          $("#content").addClass("shake");
          setTimeout(function(){
            $("#content").removeClass("shake");
            $("#page1").hide();
            $("#page2").show();
          },1500);
        }); 
        $(function(){
            $('.fraction > li').click(function(event) {
                var $this = $(this);
                var $v= $this.html();
                $this.html(parseInt($v) + 1);
                $this.addClass('x-flip');
                setTimeout(function(){
                    $this.removeClass('x-flip');
                }, 500);

            });
        });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
